while less immunoreaktive perikarya and somewhat less dense fiber 
network are observed in the anterodorsal part of the medial amygda-
loid nucleus (MeAD), the anterior part of the basomedial amygdala 
(BMA) and the main intercalated amygdaloid nucleus (IM). Higher 
magnification image (g) illustrates the GLP-1R-IR elements in the 
CeM. aca anterior commissure, cst commissural stria terminalis, LV 
